Hi Steve…what’s your availability for a call today?
Fred
I’m free now until 345pm est and after 430pm est

Steve,

I’ve shared your info with my friend at Denim Social, Christina Trapolino, and working to set up a call for you.  Will keep you posted

Fred
Awesome. Im ready. Thank you, Fred.

Hi Fred, I wanted to touch base. I’ve been making sure I check my personal email a few times a day so I don’t miss any intros. I’m very interested and I’m sure things are in motion but wanted you to know I’m on standby and excited to get the conversations going.

Their CFO (and the first person in the interview chain) is on PTO this week so nothing is going to happen until next week…
Hang in there…

Sounds good, Fred. 

I also went down the rabbit hole in terms of researching the other companies as well. 

Panzura under Jill Stelfox’s leadership is something I keep going back to and am interested.
K…I have a call Friday with their CRO, Dan Waldschmidt…plan on bringing up your info
